1. *Laura* je danas donela tortu. (Laura brought a cake today.)
2. Videla sam *Lauru* na pijaci juče. (I saw Laura at the market yesterday.)
3. *Laurin* pas je jako živahan. (Laura's dog is very lively.)
4. Idem kod *Laurine* sestre večeras. (I'm going to Laura's sister's tonight.)
5. *Lauri* se dopada taj momak. (Laura likes that guy.)
6. *Lauru* su pozvali na razgovor za posao. (Laura was invited for a job interview.)
7. *Laurine* oči su plave kao more. (Laura's eyes are as blue as the sea.)
8. *Lauri* je potrebna pomoć oko domaćeg zadatka. (Laura needs help with her homework.)
9. *Laurinim* roditeljima se dopada moj poklon. (Laura's parents like my gift.)
10. *Lauru* je bilo sramota zbog toga što je rekla. (Laura was ashamed of what she said.)